This paper is primarily focused on improving the representation power of 3D face models using deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of regularization and network architecture, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of proxies and dual-pathway networks, which are topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
